                    li OPEN SOFWARE
                    li ACHIEVE OUTCOMES AND GET REAL IMPACT
                    li TECHNOLOGY HAVE TO ADAPT TO HUMAN, NOT THE OTHER WAY AROUND
                p Because technology and data can’t be the ultimate goal; it is just a mean to help PEOPLE and organization to optimize their everyday actions and achieve goals.
